{"tid":1910871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"匈牙利 斯洛文尼亞 確診首宗支那肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T07:52:16.000Z","uid":223664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47bec58fc05b80b71cf0eed6f1e51cb316503f6d","tid":1910871,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】另外，多國都再有新增新型冠狀病毒確診病例，其中匈牙利和斯洛文尼亞首次出現確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n匈牙利總理歐爾班周三證實當地首次出現兩宗確診病例，兩名患者都是在當地留學的伊朗學生，近期曾經返回伊朗過年，兩人都未有出現病徵，目前正接受隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗是繼南韓和意大利後疫情最嚴重的國家，至今累計確診病例2922宗，92人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n斯洛文尼亞總理沙雷茨亦透過社交網站宣布當地出現首宗確診，患者由摩洛哥途經意大利抵達斯洛文尼亞，入境後確診感染。<br />\n<br />\n另外，伊拉克新增三宗確診，兩宗來自迪亞拉，另一宗就在納杰夫。<br />\n<br />\n而在首都巴格達就出現第二宗死亡個案，死者是一名65男人，本身患有慢性疾病。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=383071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383071&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=3ae79138\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383071&h=1bf627d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=383071</a>"},{"pid":"6d5e360b558ffc90e6e8f9bd587f0811085d030d","tid":1910871,"uid":256671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d17cbf05e2a820e4977eaceeacfab5014cc8e2","tid":1910871,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"巴爾幹都收埋皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n土佬到依加都冇真唔真"},{"pid":"66916e033eccaa0667d0f49e0403f83e59bed582","tid":1910871,"uid":223664,"like":1,"dislike":